  Read about the ActiveRecord query interface:
  http://guides.rubyonrails.org/active_record_querying.html

  Read about the request object:
  http://api.rubyonrails.org/v3.2.0/classes/ActionDispatch/Request.html

  Read about ActiveRecord associations:
  http://api.rubyonrails.org/classes/ActiveRecord/Associations/ClassMethods.html#method-i-has_many

  Read about Rails routing:
  http://guides.rubyonrails.org/routing.html

  Read about hacking a subselect in ActiveRecord:
  http://pivotallabs.com/users/jsusser/blog/articles/567-hacking-a-subselect-in-activerecord

  Read about the state machine in Rails:
  https://www.google.com/search?q=state+machines+in+rails

  Read about full text search on Heroku:
  https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/full-text-search

